Daytona_Beach.Seabreeze High School:
Seabreeze High School is a public high school located in Daytona Beach, Florida. The school was named a Blue Ribbon School of Excellence in 1989. 


== Notable alumni ==
Duane and Gregg Allman, of The Allman Brothers Band, class of 1965
Bill France, Jr., president of NASCAR from 1972 to 2000, class of 1951.
